<Topics>
	<Topic Name="MISC_FIRST_CONTACT">
		<Dialogue>
			<Speaker Name="Drengin">1</Speaker>
			<Listener Name="Human">0</Listener>
			<Phrase>
				<Morality>2</Morality>
				<Text>Finally, the human race is about to be crushed. Any last words, [YourLeaderName]?</Text>
			</Phrase>
		</Dialogue>
		<Dialogue>
			<Speaker Name="Arcean">3</Speaker>
			<Listener Name="Human">0</Listener>
			<Phrase>
				<Morality>1</Morality>
				<Text>Our backs are against the wall, friend. There is nothing more to do but try to take out as many Drengin and Yor fleets as possible before we're overwhelmed.
We are proud to have fought alongside the humans, [YourLeaderName].</Text>
			</Phrase>
		</Dialogue>
		<Dialogue>
			<Speaker Name="Altarian">2</Speaker>
			<Listener Name="Human">0</Listener>
			<Phrase>
				<Morality>0</Morality>
				<Text>Hope is lost, cousin. The Drengin have our forces outnumbered and our planets are falling quickly before their onslaught.
Save Earth before it's too late!</Text>
			</Phrase>
		</Dialogue>
		<Dialogue>
			<Speaker Name="Torian">4</Speaker>
			<Listener Name="Human">0</Listener>
			<Phrase>
				<Morality>0</Morality>
				<Text>They've done it again. Those vile Drengin have enslaved a majority of the Torian population, and rule over them without mercy or compassion.

I really do hate them, [YourLeaderName]. Why can't they just die?</Text>
			</Phrase>
		</Dialogue>
		<Dialogue>
			<Speaker Name="Yor">5</Speaker>
			<Listener Name="Human">0</Listener>
			<Phrase>
				<Morality>2</Morality>
				<Text>Earth cannot be saved, human. Death awaits your species.</Text>
			</Phrase>
		</Dialogue>
		<Dialogue>
			<Speaker Name="Iconian">9</Speaker>
			<Listener Name="Human">0</Listener>
			<Phrase>
				<Morality>0</Morality>
				<Text>This evil spreads through the galaxy like a virus. Forces from the Drengin and Yor alliance have taken over most of our worlds.
The hour is dark, human.</Text>
			</Phrase>
		</Dialogue>
